  "description": "KawaiiCon — \"det lille con-et med det store hjertet\" — is a cosplay event located in Porsgrunn at the cultural venue Ælvespeilet. The convention emphasises samhold, hygge, skaperglede og godt humør (community, coziness, creative joy and good spirits).\n\nProgramming covers anime, manga, comics, film, gaming and related interests. The convention deliberately avoids a fixed yearly theme so attendees can cosplay whatever they want or simply come as themselves.\n\nFounded in 2012 by Sara Henriksen, KawaiiCon now runs with more than 60 dedicated volunteers each year.",
